<li id="cite_note-56"><b><a href="#cite_ref-56" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.orthodoxytoday.org/articles/ChukovskayaSolzhenitsyn.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.orthodoxytoday.org/articles/ChukovskayaSolzhenitsyn.htm" rel="nofollow">Interview with Solzhenitsyn about "200 Years Together"</a> Lydia Chukovskaya, OrthodoxyToday.com January 1-7 2003.</li>
</ol>
